title: German Shepherd Rumor celebrates winning Westminster's Best in Show
text: German Shepherd Rumor celebrates winning Westminster's Best in Show Rumor, a German shepherd, leaps to lick her handler and co-owner Kent Boyles on the face after winning Best in Show at the 141st Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show.
